name: VOXELFINE #5: "Wanderer above the Sea of Fog" by Caspar David Friedrich 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: In college, I took a course on Romanticism and this painting was the image used for the flyer. It was a lot of fun to work with this angle in voxels! Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
